= [[SahrisWiki]] Requirements =
//Software Dependencies//

[[SahrisWiki]] requires and depends on the following software:
* [[http://www.python.org|Python]]
* [[http://bitbucket.org/prologic/circuits/|circuits]] //Application Server//
* [[http://mercurial.selenic.com/|Mercurial]] //Wiki Storage//
* [[http://www.sqlalchemy.org/|SQLAlchemy]] //Meta Data Storage//
* [[http://genshi.edgewall.org/|genshi]] //Templates//
* [[http://code.google.com/p/feedformatter/|feedformatter]] //RSS/Atom Feeds//
* [[http://code.google.com/p/argparse/|argparse]] //CLI Options//
* [[http://docutils.sourceforge.net/|docutils]] //reStructuredText Support//
* [[http://pygments.org/|pygments]] //Syntax Highlighting//
* [[http://pyinotify.sourceforge.net/|pyinotify]] //File System Monitoring//

All of these dependencies should automatically get installed when you isntall
[[SahrisWiki]]. If not, most of them can be instaleld by simply issueing
the command:

<<code lang="sh">>
$ pip install foo
<</code>>

[[SahrisWiki]] also integrate the following libraries:
* [[http://code.google.com/p/creoleparser/|creoleparser-0.7.2]] //Wiki Parser//

Please ensure that they are installed and working correctly and install each
dependency either by following it's installation instructions or by isntalling
using your package manager.
